dialog.body: Hello, thank you for contacting Old Stone Auto Insurance. My name is Mark Griffin. May I have your name, please?
Sure, my name is Elizabeth Stewart.
Great, thank you, Elizabeth. Can you please provide me with your policy number for identification purposes?
Yes, my policy number is five six seven eight nine.
Thank you, Elizabeth. Additionally, could you verify the mailing address associated with your policy?
Of course, the address on file is one two three Main Street, Cityville.
Thank you for confirming that, Elizabeth. Is there anything else I can assist you with today?
I just wanted to check the status of my recent claim. Can you provide an update on that?
Certainly, let me look that up for you. Thank you for your patience, Elizabeth.
I have checked your claim status, and it is currently being processed. Thank you for reaching out, Elizabeth. Have a great day!
